Cheatsheet

unwelcomed <- read_csv("https://raw.githubusercontent.com/agricolamz/DS_for_DH/master/data/death_of_migrants_and_refugees_from_the_Unwelcomed_project.csv")
## Rows: 5506 Columns: 10
##  Column specification 
## Delimiter: ","
## chr (6): date, location, collapsed_region, region, collapsed_cause, cause_of...
## dbl (4): id, total_death_missing, lat, lon
## 
##  Use `spec()` to retrieve the full column specification for this data.
##  Specify the column types or set `show_col_types = FALSE` to quiet this message.
unwelcomed %>% 
  leaflet() %>% 
  addCircles(lng = ~lon, 
             lat = ~lat)
unwelcomed %>% 
  leaflet() %>% 
  addTiles() %>% 
  addCircles(lng = ~lon,
             lat = ~lat)
pal_cat <- colorFactor("Set3", domain = unwelcomed$collapsed_cause)
pal_cat(unwelcomed$collapsed_cause[1])
## [1] "#D9D9D9"
RColorBrewer::display.brewer.all()

unwelcomed %>% 
  filter(str_detect(date, "2014")) %>% 
  leaflet() %>% 
  addTiles() %>% 
  addCircles(lng = ~lon,
             lat = ~lat,
             label = ~total_death_missing, 
             color  = ~pal_cat(collapsed_cause), 
             opacity = 0.9,
             popup = ~cause_of_death) %>%  
  addLegend(pal = pal_cat,
            values = ~collapsed_cause,
            title = "")
unwelcomed %>% 
  filter(str_detect(date, "2014")) %>% 
  leaflet() %>% 
  addProviderTiles("Stamen.TonerLite") %>% 
  addCircles(lng = ~lon,
             lat = ~lat,
             label = ~total_death_missing, 
             color  = ~pal_cat(collapsed_cause), 
             opacity = 0.9,
             popup = ~cause_of_death) %>%  
  addLegend(pal = pal_cat,
            values = ~collapsed_cause,
            title = "")

https://leaflet-extras.github.io/leaflet-providers/preview/index.html

We can save a map into a variable:

unwelcomed %>% 
  filter(str_detect(date, "2014")) %>% 
  leaflet() %>% 
  addProviderTiles("Stamen.TonerLite") %>% 
  addCircles(lng = ~lon,
             lat = ~lat,
             label = ~total_death_missing, #     
             color  = ~pal_cat(collapsed_cause), #   
             opacity = 0.9,
             popup = ~cause_of_death) %>%  #    ,    
  addLegend(pal = pal_cat,
            values = ~collapsed_cause,
            title = "2014") ->
  m_2014

unwelcomed %>% 
  filter(str_detect(date, "2015")) %>% 
  leaflet() %>% 
  addProviderTiles("Stamen.TonerLite") %>% 
  addCircles(lng = ~lon,
             lat = ~lat,
             label = ~total_death_missing, #     
             color  = ~pal_cat(collapsed_cause), #   
             opacity = 0.9,
             popup = ~cause_of_death) %>%  #    ,    
  addLegend(pal = pal_cat,
            values = ~collapsed_cause,
            title = "2015") ->
  m_2015
